 tyveriene skjedde, opplyser operasjonslederen.", "Det vil n\u00e5 bli opp til politijurist om den p\u00e5grepne mannen i tjue\u00e5rene skal fremstilles for varetektsfengsling mandag."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "fe0bdc42c4b69e24814050ca6f200b3796a83bf8130aa7e7b5afd40ab69cfe2b"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-18T13:37:03.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "F\u00f8rer i stj\u00e5let bil med falske skilter, fremsto som ruset."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article14258994.ece/yoadix/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_0697.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/db85f73f404f5758bc05d5ba2c41e8fddd5f06eb.jpg?5988e27d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Stoppet med spikermatte i Verdal -adressa.no", "R\u00f8mte i h\u00f8y fart", "- Resolutt inngripen", "Trolig ruset", "Bileier ante ingenting", "Unders\u00f8ker bilen l\u00f8rdag"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "db85f73f404f5758bc05d5ba2c41e8fddd5f06eb"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Verdal", "Sandvika", "\u00c5dalsvollen", "Kontroll", "Tollvesenet", "tollregion midt-norge", "Politiet", "biljakt"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Verdal,Sandvika,\u00c5dalsvollen,Kontroll,Tollvesenet,tollregion midt-norge,Politiet,biljakt"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": ["automotive", "law-government-and-politics"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bil", "politi", "h\u00f8y fart"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["innherred", "w. det", "sandvika og fv", "adresseavisen", "\u00e5re-duved", "vuku"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["sverige", "sandvika", "verdal", "nord-tr\u00f8ndelag", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-